Question is in ep 5 of think like a coder by ted-ed

measure the size of the portrait in pixels
save size
number each pixels according to its row and column

coutn loop begins, count 1 to size
	check if row and column are same
		if yes then paint it
loop ends

count loop begins, count 1 to size
	check if row + column == size + 1
		if yes paint it
loop ends
